extends layout.pug

block head
    title Privacy Policy - Get Sober Spokane

block content
    // Page Header
    header.page-header.bg-primary.text-white.py-5.mt-5
        .container.px-4.px-lg-5.text-center
            h1.display-4.fw-bold Privacy Policy
            p.lead Last updated: January 2025

    // Privacy Policy Content
    section.page-section.py-5
        .container.px-4.px-lg-5
            .row.justify-content-center
                .col-lg-8
                    .content
                        h2.mb-4 Introduction
                        p
                            | Get Sober Spokane ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website and use our services.

                        h2.mb-4 Information We Collect
                        h3.h5.mb-3 Personal Information
                        p
                            | We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when you:
                        ul
                            li Contact us through our contact form
                            li Sign up for our services
                            li Request information about our programs
                            li Participate in our community activities

                        p
                            | The personal information we collect may include:
                        ul
                            li Name
                            li Email address
                            li Phone number
                            li Messages or communications you send to us

                        h3.h5.mb-3 Automatically Collected Information
                        p
                            | When you visit our website, we may automatically collect certain information about your device, including:
                        ul
                            li IP address
                            li Browser type and version
                            li Operating system
                            li Pages visited
                            li Time spent on pages
                            li Referring website

                        h2.mb-4 How We Use Your Information
                        p
                            | We use the information we collect to:
                        ul
                            li Respond to your inquiries and provide support
                            li Connect you with appropriate recovery resources
                            li Improve our website and services
                            li Send you relevant information about our programs
                            li Comply with legal obligations
                            li Protect against fraud and abuse

                        h2.mb-4 Information Sharing and Disclosure
                        p
                            | We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except in the following circumstances:
                        ul
                            li
                                strong Service Providers: 
                                | We may share information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our website and providing services (such as Formspree for contact form processing)
                            li
                                strong Legal Requirements: 
                                | We may disclose information if required by law or to protect our rights and safety
                            li
                                strong Emergency Situations: 
                                | In emergency situations where someone's safety is at risk, we may share information with appropriate authorities

                        h2.mb-4 Third-Party Services
                        p
                            | Our website uses the following third-party services:
                        ul
                            li
                                strong Formspree: 
                                | Processes our contact form submissions. Please review their 
                                a(href='https://formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy/', target='_blank') privacy policy
                                | .
                            li
                                strong Google Fonts: 
                                | Provides web fonts. Google may collect usage data. Please review their 
                                a(href='https://policies.google.com/privacy', target='_blank') privacy policy
                                | .
                            li
                                strong Bootstrap CDN: 
                                | Provides CSS and JavaScript libraries.

                        h2.mb-4 Data Security
                        p
                            | We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

                        h2.mb-4 Your Rights
                        p
                            | You have the right to:
                        ul
                            li Access the personal information we hold about you
                            li Request correction of inaccurate information
                            li Request deletion of your personal information
                            li Opt out of communications from us
                            li File a complaint with relevant authorities

                        h2.mb-4 Children's Privacy
                        p
                            | Our website is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.

                        h2.mb-4 Changes to This Privacy Policy
                        p
                            | We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.

                        h2.mb-4 Contact Us
                        p
                            | If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us:
                        .contact-info
                            p
                                strong Get Sober Spokane
                            p
                                i.bi-phone.me-2
                                | (509) 389-9350
                            p
                                i.bi-envelope.me-2
                                a(href='mailto:getsoberspokane@outlook.com' onclick="gtag('event', 'email_click', {event_category: 'contact'})") getsoberspokane@outlook.com
